    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund paid leave for those who live with extremely vulnerable persons",
        "additional_details": "I live in a household of 6 people, 5 of whom are extremely vulnerable but because I work in construction and I am not vulnerable I have to continue to work, risking bringing the virus home to everyone all because I am not eligible for paid leave under shielding guidance or the Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme.",
        "background": "The Government should amend its policy for shielding the extremely vulnerable by funding paid leave for people who live with the extremely vulnerable, to help protect at risk.",
